OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FThe government has announced a series
OL,7,Fof financial measures aimed at
OL,8,Fsupporting local councils.
OL,10,FThis includes a new Recovery Grant and
OL,11,Fadditional funding to offset the cost
OL,12,Fof rising National Insurance
OL,13,FContributions (NICs).
OL,15,FUnder the provisional local government
OL,16,Ffinance settlement for 2024 to 2025,
OL,17,Fcouncils will receive #515 million in
OL,18,Fcompensation for increased NICs,
OL,19,Fhelping to alleviate direct cost
OL,20,Fpressures.
