OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FThe Local Government Association (LGA)
OL,7,Fhad raised concerns about the impact
OL,8,Fof the increase in employer National
OL,9,FInsurance Contributions (NICs) on
OL,10,Fparish and town councils.
OL,12,FThe new funding will be incorporated
OL,13,Finto Core Spending Power in the final
OL,14,Fsettlement, alongside the introduction
OL,15,Fof a new Recovery Grant.
