OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FCllr Louise Gittins, Chair of the
OL,7,FLocal Government Association (LGA),
OL,8,Fwelcomed the announcement but
OL,9,Fexpressed concern that the funding
OL,10,Fwill still fall short of the #637
OL,11,Fmillion estimated to cover all NICs-
OL,12,Frelated costs.
OL,14,FShe noted that indirect cost
OL,15,Fincreases, such as those borne by
OL,16,Fcommissioned care providers, could
OL,17,Ftotal an additional #1.13 billion next
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
