OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FShe said: "It is good that the
OL,7,FGovernment has provided details of how
OL,8,Fit will compensate councils for direct
OL,9,Fcosts they will face through increases
OL,10,Fin employer National Insurance
OL,11,FContributions (ENICs).
OL,13,F"However, this falls short of what we
OL,14,Fhave estimated it will cost councils
OL,15,Fnext year."
