OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FThe funding forms part of a wider
OL,7,Fpackage of measures aimed at tackling
OL,8,Fchallenges such as adult and
OL,9,Fchildren's social care, homelessness
OL,10,Fprevention, and support for children
OL,11,Fwith special educational needs and
OL,12,Fdisabilities.
OL,14,FHowever, Gittins warned many councils
OL,15,Fwould still be forced to raise council
OL,16,Ftax and make cuts to vital services to
OL,17,Fbalance their budgets.
