OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FCllr John Cotton, Leader of Birmingham
OL,7,FCity Council, also welcomed the
OL,8,Fgovernment's efforts, describing the
OL,9,Fsettlement as a turning point.
OL,11,FHe emphasised the importance of
OL,12,Fadditional funding for homelessness,
OL,13,Fwhich will provide #17.7 million to
OL,14,Ftackle the crisis in Birmingham.
