OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FHe said: "Today's news demonstrates
OL,7,Fthe difference that a Labour
OL,8,FGovernment makes. The increase to our
OL,9,Ffunding will further help to put the
OL,10,Fcouncil back onto the path to
OL,11,Ffinancial sustainability and deliver
OL,12,Fthe services our residents need."
OL,14,FDespite these positive steps, both
OL,15,Fleaders acknowledged the ongoing
OL,16,Fdifficulties councils face in
OL,17,Faddressing rising costs and demand
OL,18,Fpressures.
