OL,3,CHow will the government cover National
OL,4,CInsurance rise for councils?
OL,6,FThe government's spending review,
OL,7,Fwhich includes a commitment to multi-
OL,8,Fyear settlements, will be critical in
OL,9,Fdetermining the long-term
OL,10,Fsustainability of local government
OL,11,Ffunding.
OL,13,FThe methodology behind the provisional
OL,14,Fsettlement, including details on how
OL,15,Fthe Recovery Grant will be allocated,
OL,16,Fremains under review.
OL,18,FBirmingham City Council has confirmed
OL,19,Fit is analysing the specific impacts
OL,20,Fof the settlement on its finances for
OL,21,F2025/26.
